Manual observations on the effects upon other muscles when FDP activation is kept above 0.2: - FDS becomes constrained between .09 and 0.16, with middle 50% of solutions in a range spanning only .02697 (between .13190 and .10493) - EDC goes from being redundant (with bounds of 0 and 1), to being only in the upper half (0.5 to 0.88)
